high_descs: turn around and walk over to the coffee maker in the left corner of the room
grab the coffee cup from the coffee maker
turn right and walk forwards to the microwave
place the coffee cup in the microwave and microwave it, then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the coffee maker in the corner again
place the coffee cup under the spout of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved cup under the spout of the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn left then right to face the coffee machine
Grab the cup from the coffee machine.
Turn around back to the coffee machine.
Place the cup back in the machine.
anns.task_desc: Place the warm cup in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Pick up the the mug on the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.
